READ ME FIRSTNLib3DO

The version of Lib3DO in the Toolkit1.5 release is a Beta version. The library is migrating to the Portfolio CD-ROM. 
Hardcopy documentation is not included in this release. Instead, you find the following online documentation in this folder: 
*	Lib3DO.docNASCII file containing all functions and structures. 
*	Lib3DOHelpNMPW 411 Help file. Place this file into the folder in which your MPW Help files reside. 
*	Lib3DOHelp.indexNMPW 411 Help index file. Place this file into the folder in which your MPW Help files reside. 
Hardcopy documentation will be included with the next version of the library in the Winter Portfolio release. 
